经济压力和精神包袱，不允许依靠父母积蓄买房买车。 如果违反结婚标准，视为违背企业价值观，自违反之日起 12 个月内，只享有法定的劳动报酬及福利待遇，不享有公司给予的超出法定之外的各项奖励及福利。于东来宣布在胖东来不允许夫妻间家暴冷暴力！员工不能打孩子 - DoNews"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-00327b8e22fe29007014b13a3a16c2e1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/9469534937"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI16j74o686PABEAMaCTExMjg3MDM0OSCQqZK8BjAAOElAC3IKOTQ2OTUzNDkzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1736748982.703676", "card_id": "Q_8947756903", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 130}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场上，为何总说「辞职」的人没走，但毫无声响的人却走了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-51037cafa3a30d9bb17f4ab9457ba3a8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8947756903"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI16j74o686PABEAMaCTExMjc2NTk5MiCOxvK7BjAAOMYBQAxyCjg5NDc3NTY5MDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1736748982.703975", "card_id": "Q_9205938149", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "研究生毕业后你们还会和导师联系吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "好多研究生毕业以后，还是和自己的老师保持一个良好的互动，你怎么样呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-742d0dc326d83b7b73e6055e7ec4ce0a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/9205938149"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI16j74o686PABEAMaCTExMjgxNzc0OCC/noG8BjAAODtADXIKOTIwNTkzODE0OXgAqgEJYmls